\f2\b0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \strokec2 To capture the lucrative Melbourne market, the digital strategy must transition from generic, high-volume keyword targeting to a localized, intent-driven "Neighborhood Authority" and "Topic Cluster" architecture.
\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf4 \super \strokec4 3
\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \nosupersub \strokec2  Targeting broad terms such as "mortgage broker" yields exceptionally low conversion rates due to hyper-competition from major banking institutions and national brokerage franchises. Instead, the architectural hierarchy should prioritize specialized, localized intent.
\f3\fs24 \cf0 \strokec3 \
