\f2\b0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \strokec2 Visual assets, particularly large hero images or team photographs, are consistently the primary culprits behind degraded Largest Contentful Paint metrics. The technical optimization process must include a comprehensive overhaul of the media library.
\f3\fs24 \cf0 \strokec3 \

\f2\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \strokec2 All existing legacy image formats, such as JPEG and PNG, must be systematically converted to next-generation formats including WebP or AVIF.
