\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \nosupersub \strokec2  These modern formats utilize superior compression algorithms that reduce file sizes by up to eighty percent without introducing any perceptible loss in visual fidelity. Furthermore, the website code must natively support lazy loading functionality. This technique defers the downloading and rendering of off-screen images until the user scrolls them into the active viewport, thereby prioritizing the bandwidth for the critical above-the-fold content and text rendering.
