\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \nosupersub \strokec2  The implementation of a persistent, sticky Call-to-Action button\'97such as "Request a Free Assessment" or "Call Now"\'97that remains affixed to the bottom of the mobile viewport as the user scrolls ensures that the primary conversion pathway is never more than a single tap away.
\fs19\fsmilli9600 \cf4 \super \strokec4 11
